# LNCVS environment configuration — copy to `.env` and fill in real values.
# The real `.env` is git-ignored and must never be committed.
#
# Which keys you need depends on which path you run:
#   - Graph LLM extraction & claim decomposition use Gemini (google-genai).
#   - The LLM fact verifier (H7) and the G2 extraction baseline use OpenAI.
#   - Sentence-Transformers / cross-encoder models download from HuggingFace
#     (a token is only needed for gated/private models; usually optional).
#
# All real runs are cache-backed: once results/*cache*.jsonl exist, the
# pipeline replays them with zero API calls and no key is required.

OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here
HUGGINGFACE_API_KEY=your-huggingface-token-here
